## Overview

These 6 flows define the corrected user journey through DealForge AI to achieve 100% replication of a PE/consulting analyst. They cover the complete lifecycle: from deal creation with stage selection, through provenance-tracked agent execution, to auditable analyst-grade reports.

All 4 existing entry paths (Chat Pipeline, Full Workflow, OFAS Mission, Direct Agent Run) converge on the same agent execution layer — meaning these flow corrections improve every path simultaneously.

### Design Decisions (agreed)


| Decision                   | Choice                                                                                           |
| -------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| Provenance surfacing       | All three layers: inline in agent output, separate audit ledger, and source footnotes in reports |
| Cross-agent contradictions | Soft warning — log and continue, surface in results and reports                                  |
| Missing data in reports    | Estimates with disclosure — labeled `[ESTIMATED]` with methodology                               |
| Deal stage selection       | User-selected — optional, defaults to "deep_dive" for backward compatibility                     |


